The paper discusses progress in AI and suggests ways to model it more rigorously. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper is directly related to AI. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses algorithmic improvements in AI. cs.RO (Robotics) is relevant as the paper discusses the role of human inputs in enabling AI capabilities. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper discusses the relationships between different sub-fields of AI. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper discusses the role of hardware speed increases in AI progress.
